name: SoliSnek
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.
The smart-contract owner can mint new tokens, please proceed with caution.

description.en: SNEK is the native token for the brand new Solidly platform on AVAX, SoliSnek - as all solidly tokens are, it will be the cornerstone for the new liquidity layer for AVAX allowing users to buy it, lock it and vote with it making a robust system for the next generation of DeFi on avalanche
